Project settings control certain metadata of a Pvideo Project, like the name and thumbnail, as well as some general layout and audio settings. This provides a convenient way to configure global settings for a Project.

The Project settings consist of a pop-up dialog with three tabs:

- **General settings:** Project name, Thumbnail, UUID

- **Layout &amp; Sound settings:** Global layout and audio settings

- **Advanced settings:** Analytics tracking

## General settings tab
This tab of the Project settings provides options to change the following parameters:

- [**Project name**](/doxee-platform/docs/pvideo-designer-project-name)

- [**Thumbnail**](/doxee-platform/docs/pvideo-designer-thumbnail)

- [**UUID**](/doxee-platform/docs/pvideo-designer-project-uuidcopy)

![project_settings_general.png](data:image/png;base64,)Project settings &gt; General

## Layout &amp; Sound settings tab
This tab of the Project settings provides options to change the following parameters:

- [**Aspect ratio**](/doxee-platform/docs/pvideo-designer-aspect-ratio)

- [**Color palette**](/doxee-platform/docs/pvideo-designer-color-palette)

- [**Fonts**](/doxee-platform/docs/pvideo-designer-fonts)

- [**Soundtrack**](/doxee-platform/docs/pvideo-designer-soundtrack)

![project_settings_layout and sound.png](data:image/png;base64,)&amp; Sound Project settings &gt; Layout &amp; Sound

## Advanced settings tab
This tab of the Project settings provides options to change the following parameters:

- [**Analytics tracking**](/doxee-platform/docs/pvideo-designer-enable-analytics-tracking-for-pvideo)

![project_settings_advanced.png](data:image/png;base64,)Project settings &gt; Advanced

Read on to find out more about the granular setting options.
